DOCs:
=====

See doc\ directory.

If you're searching for "full" docs ...

- in english: please be patient and frequest BDOC_260.ZIP until translation
              of BT-XE manuals to english is completed

- in german:  please frequest magic BTXE_DOK to get the *.INF / *.DOC full
              docs of BT-XE.
              

EXEs and related:
=================

maxcomm\*    BT32 exe for use with maxcomm.dll
async_os\*   BT32 exe with internal 32bit async routines - if you have
             problems with it, then try the maxcomm version!
common\*     stuff needed for both - copy these files to the Binkley
             directory, too

bt*.exe      BT-XE mailer exe, internal async and maxcomm versions
btutil*.exe  BT-XE utility (replaces btctl* and btlng*)
bt*.sym      BT-XE symbol information - please put this in same directory
             as the *.EXE file
language.txt BT-XE mixed language text: english, star trek, german
maxcomm.dll  MAXCOMM.DLL v2.90.1 (COMM DLL for BT-XE, Maximus etc.)
mcp32.dll    MCP32.DLL of Maximus 3.xx

             
CONFIGs:
========

See thomas\ directory for my full and working configs.


COST TABLES FOR GERMANY:
========================

Not included (they are very large). If you want the complete collection of
inner germany cost tables, then frequest magic BTXE_CST ...


FOR SOFTWARE DEVELOPERS:
========================

developr\*   stuff interesting for software developers

